Method Detail

getMessageStateSummary

List<MessageReportDto> getMessageStateSummary(Date startDate,
                                              Date endDate)
Returns list of aggregated values about messages in specified time interval. Messages are aggregated and also ordered by service, operation name, source system and state.

Parameters:
startDate - Start date (starts at 0.00)
endDate - End date (ends at 23.59)
Returns:
result list MessageReportDto
